    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td>Beginner</td>
            <td>Entry-level DSLR or mirrorless (e.g., Canon Rebel / Sony a6000)</td>
            <td>18–55mm kit lens</td>
            <td>Learning exposure, family events, casual photography</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Enthusiast</td>
