<h2>Accessories to consider</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Sturdy tripod for long exposures and night photography.</li>
    <li>Extra batteries and memory cards.</li>
    <li>Camera bag with weather protection.</li>
    <li>Lens cleaning kit (blower, microfiber cloth, lens solution).</li>
    <li>External flash or LED light for indoor portraits.</li>
</ul>
